title: Burger.Bar.To.Gourmet.Star.S01E01.HDTV.x264-TVCUK.mp4
description:
Britain boasts some of the best chefs and restaurants in the world. But it's also home to some of the worst food on the planet. In this new series, a selection of fast food cooks with no formal training are given the opportunity of a lifetime: to be taught by some of the country's most refined chefs, and fast-tracked through years of tough training in just weeks. If that's not enough, the chefs must then pose as seasoned professionals, cooking in world class kitchens.




Burger Bar To Gourmet Star - Series 1, Episode 1



Carl at Midsummer House, Cambridge

Burger-van owner Carl is trained up by perfectionist chef Danile Clifford.




Original Air Date: 24-Mar-2015
